text: Tauxières-Mutry is a former commune. It is in Grand Est in the Marne department in northeast France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Val de Livre.Arrêté préfectoral 18 November 2015 == Related pages == * Communes of the Marne department == References == Category:Former communes in Marne
title: Tauxières-Mutry
